OL,3,CServices back to normal at Manchester
OL,4,CPiccadilly after overnight repairs
OL,6,FNetwork Rail say services will be back
OL,7,Fto normal after overhead wires were
OL,8,Ffinally repaired at Manchester
OL,9,FPiccadilly.
OL,11,FThere'd been disruption to services
OL,12,Fsince an incident which saw overhead
OL,13,Fwires damaged on Thursday.
OL,15,FThe delays and cancellations led to
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Mayor calling for
OL,17,Furgent answers from the rail operator,
OL,18,Fon a busy weekend for the city, with
OL,19,Fhigh profile football matches and the
OL,20,FManchester Marathon taking place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
