OL,3,CServices back to normal at Manchester
OL,4,CPiccadilly after overnight repairs
OL,6,FOn Sunday, Network Rail confirmed that
OL,7,Fteams worked throughout the night to
OL,8,Ffix the high-voltage cables on the
OL,9,Fapproach to the North West's busiest
OL,10,Frailway station after last week's
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FIt happened after a stretch of the
OL,14,Fwires were caught and damaged on a
OL,15,Fpassing train, causing major delays
OL,16,Ffor passengers for three days.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
