SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776600665
OL,3,CServices back to normal at Manchester
OL,4,CPiccadilly after overnight repairs
OL,6,FRail bosses say that with over 400
OL,7,Fmetres of damaged lines, an extended
OL,8,F12-hour closure of the railway was
OL,9,Fneeded for overhead line specialists
OL,10,Fto carry out the urgent repairs.
OL,12,FThe railway fully reopened at 11am on
OL,13,FSunday. However, passengers are still
OL,14,Fbeing urged to check services before
OL,15,Fthey travel at www.nationalrail.co.uk
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
