OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1776600665
OL,3,CServices back to normal at Manchester
OL,4,CPiccadilly after overnight repairs
OL,6,FChris Wright, Network Rail North West
OL,7,Froute director, said: "I'm sorry to
OL,8,Fpassengers who've been impacted by the
OL,9,Fdisruption since the overhead lines
OL,10,Ffailed at Manchester Piccadilly on
OL,11,FThursday. Since that happened our
OL,12,Fteams of engineers have been working
OL,13,Faround the clock to repair the damaged
OL,14,F400-metre stretch of high-voltage
OL,15,Fwires which provide power to electric
OL,16,Ftrains.
